item.title: CVE-2021-21661|2024-08-03T18:23:27.518Z -- jenkins%20project -- jenkins%20kubernetes%20cli%20plugin
item.description: Jenkins Kubernetes CLI Plugin 1.10.0 and earlier does not perform permission checks in several HTTP endpoints, allowing attackers with Overall/Read permission to enumerate credentials IDs of credentials stored in Jenkins.
